        "id": 3, "category_id": 1, "sort": 3, "visible": true, "created_at": "2016-08-01T22:06:51.625+08:00", "updated_at": "2016-08-02T00:11:28.316+08:00", "title_en": "Strategy", "title_zh_cn": "战略思想", "title_zh_tw": "戰略思想", "body_en": "\u003cp style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://en.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/zhanlue_en.png\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n", "body_zh_cn": "\u003cp style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" height=\"448\" src=\"http://www.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/56dd4b11/zhanlue_news.png\" width=\"441\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n", "body_zh_tw": "\u003cp style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" height=\"448\" src=\"http://tc.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/56dd4adb/zhanlue_tc.png\" width=\"441\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n", "url": "strategy", "slug": "strategy"
    },
    {
        "id": 4, "category_id": 1, "sort": 4, "visible": true, "created_at": "2016-08-02T00:14:34.266+08:00", "updated_at": "2016-08-02T00:14:34.266+08:00", "title_en": "Investment Strengths", "title_zh_cn": "公司优势", "title_zh_tw": "公司優勢", "body_en": "\u003cp\u003eGolden Concord Holdings Limited(hereinafter referred to as \u0026ldquo;GCL\u0026rdquo;), parent company of GCL New Energy, is a leader in the energy industry and has nearly 20 years of power operating experience. As China\u0026#39;s largest non state-owned power company, GCL has accumulated a wealth of development, construction, operation and maintenance experience in solar, wind, biomass and other fields. It is China\u0026#39;s first PV system integrator and first energy management contract (EMC) enterprise, China\u0026rsquo;s largest PV power plant developer in the United States, and the solar enterprise with the largest investment in Africa. In the photovoltaic industry, GCL enjoys a high reputation and was elected Chairman of Asian Photovoltaic Industry Association (APVIA).\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eGCL possesses a strong technological innovation capability. In the PV materials manufacturing field, GCL has high-purity polysilicon and series of high efficient wafers manufactured with own proprietary technologies, always leading the industry\u0026#39;s progress. With PV products of higher conversion efficiency and lower cost as well as highly optimized PV systems provided by GCL Group, GCL New Energy enjoys unique advantage in its construction of efficient and quality power plants as well as its research and integration of new energy applications.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://en.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/supimg.jpg\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n", "body_zh_cn": "\u003cp\u003e协鑫新能源的母公司\u0026mdash;\u0026mdash;协鑫集团以清洁能源、新能源及相关产业为主的国际化综合性能源集团，是全球领先的光伏材料制造商及新能源开发与运营商，在太阳能、风能、生物质能等领域，积累了丰富的开发、建设及运维经验。协鑫是中国最早的光伏系统集成商和最早的合同能源管理企业，在光伏行业内享有高度的品牌美誉，被推选为亚洲光伏协会主席单位。2015年，协鑫跻身全球新能源企业500强第11位。\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e协鑫有着强大的科技创新能力，在光伏材料制造领域，协鑫拥有自主知识产权的领先技术生产的高纯多晶硅和系列高效硅片，始终引领着行业的进步。协鑫集团为协鑫新能源提供了转换效率更高、成本更低的光伏产品和更为优化的光伏发电系统，推动协鑫新能源高效、优质的光伏电站建设以及新能源应用的研究和整合。\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/supimg.jpg\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n", "body_zh_tw": "\u003cp\u003e協鑫新能源的母公司\u0026mdash;\u0026mdash;協鑫集團是能源行業中的領軍企業，有著近二十年的電力運營經驗，是中國規模最大的非公有制電力公司，在太陽能、風能、生物質能等領域，積累了豐富的開發、建設及運營經驗。協鑫是中國最早的光伏系統集成商和最早的合同能源管理企業，是中國在美國的最大海外光伏電站開發商，也是在非洲投資最大的太陽能企業。在光伏行業內，協鑫享有高度的品牌美譽，被推選為亞洲光伏協會主席單位。\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e協鑫有著強大的科技創新能力，在光伏材料製造領域，協鑫擁有自主智慧財產權的領先技術生產的高純多晶矽和系列高效矽片，始終引領著行業的進步。協鑫集團為協鑫新能源提供了轉換效率更高、成本更低的光伏產品和更為優化的光伏發電系統，推動協鑫新能源高效、優質的光伏電站建設以及新能源應用的研究和整合。\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"http://tc.gclnewenergy.com/uploads/supimg.jpg\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n", "url": "superiority", "slug": "superiority"
    },
    {
        "id": 5, "category_id": 1, "sort": 5, "visible": true, "created_at": "2016-08-02T00:20:10.615+08:00", "updated_at": "2016-08-02T00:20:10.615+08:00", "title_en": "Corporate Governance", "title_zh_cn": "公司治理", "title_zh_tw": "公司治理", "body_en": "\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCORPORATE GOVERNANCE\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eThe board of directors (the \u0026ldquo;Board\u0026rdquo;) is committed to promoting good corporate governance to safeguard the interests of the shareholders and to enhance the Group\u0026rsquo;s performance. The Company has set up the Audit Committee, Remuneration Committee, Nomination Committee, Strategic Planning Committee and Risk Management Committee to assist the Board in focusing on specific matters. fulfil their roles and responsibilities delegated by the Board, report to the Board on decisions and actions taken, and make any necessary recommendations.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n", "body_zh_cn": "\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e公司管治\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e董事会矢志促进良好企业管治以保障股东权益及提升本集团表现。本公司已成立审核委员会、薪酬委员会、提名委员会、战略委员会及风险管理委员会，在特定专责事宜上协助董事会，履行由董事会分配的角色及责任，向董事会汇报决定及行动，并提出必需的建议。\u003c/p\u003e\r\n", "body_zh_tw": "\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e公司管治\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e董事會矢志促進良好企業管治以保障股東權益及提升本集團表現。本公司已成立審核委員會、薪酬委員會、提名委員會、戰略委員會及風險管理委員會，在特定專責事宜上協助董事會，履行由董事會分配的角色及責任，向董事會匯報決定及行動，並提出必需的建議。\u003c/p\u003e\r\n", "url": "control", "slug": "control"
    },
